[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "私、調合したいものがあるの。\nシャル、シャリー……手伝ってくれないかしら",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "90362210238560528",
		"text": "もちろんです！\nわたしでよければ、なんでもお手伝いします！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "322297020958821866",
		"text": "あたしも手伝うよ！　\nミルカのお願いなら、なんでもやっちゃうから！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "ありがとう。助かるわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……それで、調合したいものなんだけど――\nこれらの鉱石を使った、砥石よ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "322297020958821866",
		"text": "砥石？　ミルカって、砥石使うっけ？\n……あ、もしかして",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……砥石は、姉さんに渡すつもり",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "90362210238560528",
		"text": "そっか、ユリエさんの武器には砥石を使いますもんね。\n贈りもの、いいですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "322297020958821866",
		"text": "でも、どうして急に？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……姉さんはこれから、もっと色んな場所へ行く。\nこの世界でも、元の世界に帰ってからも、きっと",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "それが、姉さんの夢だったから……\nたくさんのものを見て、聞いて、物語を書いて――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "だから、これから広い世界に出ていく姉さんに、\n役立つものを贈りたいと思ったの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "90362210238560528",
		"text": "素敵です……\nミルカさんの気持ち、きっとユリエさんも喜びますよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "322297020958821866",
		"text": "ねえ、ミルカ。\nユリエさんと離れ離れになるの、寂しくない？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……別に、平気よ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……離れても、姉さんが旅先で書いた本を読めば、\n姉さんを身近に感じられるはずだから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "90362210238560528",
		"text": "ふふ……うん、そうですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "そう。姉さんの言葉や考えは、\nきっと本の中に詰まってる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "322297020958821866",
		"text": "そっか……\n本を通して、ユリエさんと繋がってるんだね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "90362210238560528",
		"text": "……わたしも、ユリエさんの本、楽しみにしています",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "322297020958821866",
		"text": "あたしも、絶対読むよ！　",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "うん。\n二人も読んでくれるなら、きっと姉さんも喜ぶ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……それじゃあ二人には、\nこっちの素材の準備をお願いするわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "90362210238560528",
		"text": "分かりました！　お任せください！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "322297020958821866",
		"text": "よーし、ミルカとユリエさんのためにも、\n頑張っちゃうぞー！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "322297020958821866",
		"text": "ねぇミルカ、ユリエさんに渡す時、\nちゃんと気持ち伝えなよ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……うるさいわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "分かってるわよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]